        <unitName xml:lang="en">metric ton*km</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Transportation distance is calculated specific for Germany. Total amount of 'Secondary raw materials; municipal wastes and other wastes' is derived from Eurostat in Million ton-km for the year of 2016. It is then divided by total Thousand tonnes to extract km. The latter one is adjusted to metric ton*km simply dy dividing with 1000. Reference: Eurostat, 2018, Summary of annual road freight transport by type of operation and type of transport (1 000 t, Mio Tkm, Mio Veh-km), Retrieved online at: http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/transport/data/database on 05 of June 2018</comment>
